is removed; critical for safety in collaborative robots and elevators."]}],"\n",["$","p","p-8",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Bundle Adjustment"}],": Optimization technique refining 3D reconstruction and camera poses from image matches; core SLAM method."]}],"\n",["$","hr","hr-2",{}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-2",{"children":"C"}],"\n",["$","p","p-9",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Chatbot (automation context)"}],": RPA application automating customer service through pre-defined conversation flows; often rule-based (not neural networks)."]}],"\n",["$","p","p-10",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Closed-Loop Control"}],": System with feedback; actual output compared to desired (reference); error signal drives corrective action. Example: cruise control."]}],"\n",["$","p","p-11",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"CMDPs (Constrained Markov Decision Processes)"}],": Reinforcement learning formulation with optimization objective AND constraint satisfaction; enables safe RL."]}],"\n",["$","p","p-12",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"CNN (Convolutional Neural Network)"}],": Deep learning architecture for vision; learns hierarchical features (edges → textures → objects) through convolution operations."]}],"\n",["$","p","p-13",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Control Barrier Functions (CBF)"}],": Mathematical certificate proving safety; if barrier function (h(s) \\geq 0), system state remains safe."]}],"\n",["$","p","p-14",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Control Theory"}],": Mathematical discipline studying feedback systems, stability, robustness; bridges continuous/discrete, linear/nonlinear systems."]}],"\n",["$","p","p-15",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Controllability"}],": Property of system; can state reach desired configuration through appropriate control inputs? Rank condition: (rank([B, AB, ..., A^{n-1}B]) = n)."]}],"\n","$L26","\n